  "id": 2123,
  "name": "Rockfond Rifthound",
  "desc": "A beast with monstrous blood that is capable of eroding the boundaries of the world. They were created by \"Gold.\"<br/>They do display certain biological behaviors similar to those of real wolves. Perhaps they feel jealousy towards these their \"next of kin,\" and dream of replacing them someday.",
