              {
                "item_values": [],
                "key": "Tutorial",
                "string_values": [
                  "This is the mature form of a Rifthound Whelp... or so it would seem. However, these monsters do not have natural life cycles, and their growth remains a mystery. The Rifthound attacks can apply stacks of the \"Corrosion\" status, which will cause all characters in the party to <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">continually lose HP</span>. Additionally, when they take elemental damage from their respective element, Rifthounds will enter an Elemental Devourer state that will allow them <span style=\"color:#FFE14BFF\">to fight more fiercely at the cost of lessened RES to that particular element</span>."
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
